WEBVTT

00:00:27.040 --> 00:00:36.560
The revelation of Jesus Christ, which God gave unto him to shew unto his servants things which must shortly come to pass.

00:00:37.180 --> 00:00:49.520
And he sent and signified it by his angel unto his servant John, who bear record of the word of God and of the testimony of Jesus Christ, and of all things that he saw.

00:00:50.580 --> 00:01:00.440
Blessed is he that readeth, and they that hear the words of this prophecy, and keep those things which are written therein, for the time is at hand.

00:01:01.580 --> 00:01:25.040
John, to the seven churches which are in Asia, grace be unto you and peace, from him which is, and which was, and which is to come, and from the seven spirits which are before his throne, and from Jesus Christ, who is the faithful witness, and the first begotten of the dead, and the prince of the kings of the earth.

00:01:25.040 --> 00:01:40.460
Unto him that loved us and washed us from our sins in his own blood, and hath made us kings and priests unto God and his Father. To him be glory and dominion for ever and ever. Amen.

00:01:41.660 --> 00:01:55.440
Behold, he cometh with clouds, and every eye shall see him, and they also which pierced him, and all kindreds of the earth shall wail because of him. Even so. Amen.

00:01:56.560 --> 00:02:09.440
I am Alpha and Omega, the beginning and the ending, saith the Lord, which is, and which was, and which is to come, the Almighty.

00:02:10.800 --> 00:02:26.080
I, John, who also am your brother and companion in tribulation, and in the kingdom and patience of Jesus Christ, was in the isle that is called Patmos, for the word of God and for the testimony of Jesus Christ.

00:02:26.080 --> 00:02:33.120
I was in the spirit on the Lord's day, and heard behind me a great voice as of a trumpet, saying,

00:02:34.080 --> 00:02:59.400
I am Alpha and Omega, the first and the last, and, what thou seest, write in a book and send it unto the seven churches which are in Asia, unto Ephesus, and unto Smyrna, and unto Pergamos, and unto Thyatira, and unto Sardis, and unto Philadelphia, and unto Laodicea.

00:03:00.160 --> 00:03:18.160
And I turned to see the voice that spake with me, and, being turned, I saw seven golden candlesticks, and in the midst of the seven candlesticks, one like unto the Son of Man, clothed with a garment down to the foot, and girt about the paps with a golden girdle.

00:03:18.160 --> 00:03:34.360
His head and his hairs were white like wool, as white as snow, and his eyes were as a flame of fire, and his feet like unto fine brass, as if they burned in a furnace, and his voice as the sound of many waters.

00:03:35.010 --> 00:03:46.760
And he had in his right hand seven stars, and out of his mouth went a sharp two-edged sword, and his countenance was as the sun shineth in his strength.

00:03:46.760 --> 00:03:55.120
And when I saw him, I fell at his feet as dead, and he laid his right hand upon me, saying unto me,

00:03:55.680 --> 00:04:11.800
Fear not! I am the first and the last. I am he that liveth and was dead, and, behold, I am alive for evermore. Amen! And have the keys of hell and of death.

00:04:11.800 --> 00:04:35.960
Write the things which thou hast seen, and the things which are, and the things which shall be hereafter. The mystery of the seven stars which thou sawest in my right hand, and the seven golden candlesticks. The seven stars are the angels of the seven churches, and the seven candlesticks which thou sawest are the seven churches.

00:05:00.928 --> 00:05:06.848
Unto the angel of the Church of Ephesus write,

00:05:07.288 --> 00:05:12.128
These things saith he that holdeth the seven stars in his right hand,

00:05:12.128 --> 00:05:16.328
Who walketh in the midst of the seven golden candlesticks.

00:05:17.028 --> 00:05:20.908
I know thy works, and thy labour, and thy patience,

00:05:21.408 --> 00:05:24.248
And how thou canst not bear them which are evil,

00:05:24.688 --> 00:05:27.988
And thou hast tried them which say they are apostles,

00:05:28.188 --> 00:05:35.008
And are not, and hast found them liars, And hast borne, and hast patience,

00:05:35.388 --> 00:05:39.808
And for my name's sake hast laboured, and hast not fainted.

00:05:40.748 --> 00:05:47.728
Nevertheless, I have somewhat against thee, Because thou hast left thy first love.

00:05:48.428 --> 00:05:54.268
Remember therefore from whence thou art fallen, And repent, and do the first works,

00:05:54.668 --> 00:06:00.828
Or else I will come unto thee quickly, And will remove thy candlestick out of his place,

00:06:01.348 --> 00:06:04.948
Except thou repent. But this thou hast,

00:06:04.948 --> 00:06:10.328
That thou hatest the deeds of the Nicolaitans, Which I also hate.

00:06:11.248 --> 00:06:16.288
He that hath an ear, let him hear What the Spirit saith unto the churches.

00:06:17.088 --> 00:06:21.668
To him that overcometh will I give to eat Of the tree of life,

00:06:21.828 --> 00:06:29.208
Which is in the midst of the paradise of God. And unto the angel of the church in Smyrna write,

00:06:29.208 --> 00:06:35.828
These things saith the first and the last, Which was dead and is alive.

00:06:36.488 --> 00:06:44.608
I know thy works and tribulation and poverty, But thou art rich, and I know the blasphemy of them

00:06:44.608 --> 00:06:49.748
Which say they are Jews and are not, But are the synagogue of Satan.

00:06:50.628 --> 00:06:56.868
Fear none of those things which thou shalt suffer. Behold, the devil shall cast some of

00:06:56.868 --> 00:07:03.508
you into prison that ye may be tried, And ye shall have tribulation ten days.

00:07:04.268 --> 00:07:09.288
Be thou faithful unto death, And I will give thee a crown of life.

00:07:10.068 --> 00:07:15.388
He that hath an ear, let him hear What the Spirit saith unto the churches.

00:07:16.188 --> 00:07:20.388
He that overcometh shall not be hurt Of the second death.

00:07:20.968 --> 00:07:24.328
And to the angel of the church in Pergamos write,

00:07:24.968 --> 00:07:29.848
These things saith he which hath the sharp sword With two edges.

00:07:30.448 --> 00:07:36.068
I know thy works and where thou dwellest, Even where Satan's seat is.

00:07:36.508 --> 00:07:41.248
And thou holdest fast my name, And hast not denied my faith,

00:07:41.628 --> 00:07:45.768
Even in those days wherein Antipas Was my faithful martyr,

00:07:46.208 --> 00:07:52.748
Who was slain among you where Satan dwelleth. But I have a few things against thee,

00:07:52.748 --> 00:07:56.608
Because thou hast there them that hold the doctrine of Balaam,

00:07:56.848 --> 00:08:01.268
Who taught Balak to cast a stumbling block Before the children of Israel,

00:08:01.488 --> 00:08:06.568
To eat things sacrificed unto idols, And to commit fornication.

00:08:07.048 --> 00:08:12.868
So hast thou also them that hold the doctrine Of the Nicolaitans, which thing I hate.

00:08:13.748 --> 00:08:20.408
Repent, or else I will come unto thee quickly, And will fight against them with the sword of my mouth.

00:08:21.128 --> 00:08:26.208
He that hath an ear, let him hear What the Spirit saith unto the churches.

00:08:27.008 --> 00:08:31.288
To him that overcometh will I give to eat of the hidden manna,

00:08:31.348 --> 00:08:36.488
And will give him a white stone, And in the stone a new name written,

00:08:36.788 --> 00:08:40.548
Which no man knoweth, saving he that receiveth it.

00:08:41.288 --> 00:08:45.008
And unto the angel of the church in Thyatira write,

00:08:45.648 --> 00:08:51.668
These things saith the Son of God, Who hath his eyes like unto a flame of fire,

00:08:51.988 --> 00:08:59.708
And his feet are like fine brass. I know thy works and charity and service and faith,

00:09:00.168 --> 00:09:05.288
And thy patience and thy works, And the last to be more than the first.

00:09:06.608 --> 00:09:09.808
Notwithstanding, I have a few things against thee,

00:09:09.808 --> 00:09:15.428
Because thou sufferest that woman Jezebel, Which calleth herself a prophetess,

00:09:15.768 --> 00:09:19.708
To teach and to seduce my servants to commit fornication,

00:09:20.128 --> 00:09:23.308
And to eat things sacrificed unto idols.

00:09:23.928 --> 00:09:29.568
And I gave her space to repent of her fornication, And she repented not.

00:09:30.408 --> 00:09:35.828
Behold, I will cast her into a bed, And them that commit adultery with her

00:09:35.828 --> 00:09:40.188
Into great tribulation, Except they repent of their deeds.

00:09:40.908 --> 00:09:47.288
And I will kill her children with death, And all the churches shall know that I am he

00:09:47.288 --> 00:09:52.648
Which searcheth the reins and hearts, And I will give unto every one of you

00:09:52.648 --> 00:09:56.588
According to your works. But unto you I say,

00:09:56.848 --> 00:10:01.408
And unto the rest in Thyatira, As many as have not this doctrine,

00:10:01.688 --> 00:10:05.408
And which have not known the depths of Satan as they speak,

00:10:05.408 --> 00:10:11.248
I will put upon you none other burden. But that which ye have already,

00:10:11.748 --> 00:10:15.828
Hold fast till I come. And he that overcometh,

00:10:15.888 --> 00:10:21.228
And keepeth my works unto the end, To him will I give power over the nations,

00:10:21.768 --> 00:10:27.708
And he shall rule them with a rod of iron, As the vessels of a potter shall they be

00:10:27.708 --> 00:10:35.288
Shivers, even as I received of my father, And I will give him the morning star.

00:10:36.208 --> 00:10:41.328
He that hath an ear, let him hear What the Spirit sayeth unto the churches.

00:10:42.788 --> 00:10:44.848
The

00:11:06.993 --> 00:11:13.253
And unto the angel of the church in Sardis write, These things saith he that hath the

00:11:13.253 --> 00:11:16.493
Seven Spirits of God and the Seven Stars.

00:11:17.013 --> 00:11:22.293
I know thy works, that thou hast a name that thou livest and art dead.

00:11:23.053 --> 00:11:28.953
Be watchful and strengthen the things which remain, that are ready to die, for I have

00:11:28.953 --> 00:11:31.873
not found thy works perfect before God.

00:11:32.713 --> 00:11:38.213
Remember therefore how thou hast received and heard, and hold fast and repent.

00:11:38.213 --> 00:11:44.753
If therefore thou shalt not watch, I will come on thee as a thief, and thou shalt not

00:11:44.753 --> 00:11:47.153
know what hour I will come upon thee.

00:11:47.953 --> 00:11:53.853
Thou hast a few names even in Sardis which have not defiled their garments, and they

00:11:53.853 --> 00:11:57.233
shall walk with me in white, for they are worthy.

00:11:58.113 --> 00:12:04.513
He that overcometh the same shall be clothed in white raiment, and I will not blot out

00:12:04.513 --> 00:12:10.873
his name out of the Book of Life, but I will confess his name before my Father and before

00:12:10.873 --> 00:12:11.993
his angels.

00:12:13.073 --> 00:12:18.233
He that hath an ear, let him hear what the Spirit saith unto the churches.

00:12:19.413 --> 00:12:26.013
And to the angel of the church in Philadelphia write, These things saith he that is holy,

00:12:26.353 --> 00:12:34.353
he that is true, he that hath the key of David, he that openeth and no man shutteth, and shutteth

00:12:34.353 --> 00:12:36.073
and no man openeth.

00:12:36.673 --> 00:12:38.193
I know thy works.

00:12:38.693 --> 00:12:46.173
Behold, I have set before thee an open door, and no man can shut it, for thou hast a little

00:12:46.173 --> 00:12:51.093
strength, and hast kept my word, and hast not denied my name.

00:12:51.853 --> 00:12:57.993
Behold, I will make them of the synagogue of Satan which say they are Jews and are not,

00:12:57.993 --> 00:12:59.453
but do lie.

00:12:59.853 --> 00:13:06.813
Behold, I will make them to come and worship before thy feet, and to know that I have loved thee.

00:13:07.353 --> 00:13:14.153
Because thou hast kept the word of my patience, I also will keep thee from the hour of temptation,

00:13:14.693 --> 00:13:19.593
which shall come upon all the world to try them that dwell upon the earth.

00:13:20.473 --> 00:13:22.353
Behold, I come quickly.

00:13:22.933 --> 00:13:27.453
Hold that fast which thou hast, that no man take thy crown.

00:13:28.253 --> 00:13:34.693
Him that overcometh will I make a pillar in the temple of my God, and he shall go no more

00:13:34.693 --> 00:13:35.173
out.

00:13:35.633 --> 00:13:42.673
And I will write upon him the name of my God, and the name of the city of my God, which

00:13:42.673 --> 00:13:49.873
is New Jerusalem, which cometh down out of heaven from my God, and I will write upon

00:13:49.873 --> 00:13:51.813
him my new name.

00:13:52.473 --> 00:13:57.473
He that hath an ear, let him hear what the Spirit saith unto the churches.

00:13:58.453 --> 00:14:06.653
And unto the angel of the church of the Laodiceans write, These things saith thee Amen, the faithful

00:14:06.653 --> 00:14:10.913
and true witness, the beginning of the creation of God.

00:14:11.593 --> 00:14:16.293
I know thy works, that thou art neither cold nor hot.

00:14:16.293 --> 00:14:19.213
I would thou wert cold or hot.

00:14:19.613 --> 00:14:27.253
So then because thou art lukewarm and neither cold nor hot, I will spew thee out of my mouth,

00:14:27.673 --> 00:14:35.233
because thou sayest, I am rich and increased with goods and have need of nothing, and knowest

00:14:35.233 --> 00:14:41.953
not that thou art wretched and miserable and poor and blind and naked.

00:14:42.653 --> 00:14:49.533
I counsel thee to buy of me gold tried in the fire that thou mayest be rich, and white

00:14:49.533 --> 00:14:55.533
raiment that thou mayest be clothed, and that the shame of thy nakedness do not appear,

00:14:56.133 --> 00:15:00.673
and anoint thine eyes with eye-sav that thou mayest see.

00:15:01.473 --> 00:15:04.893
As many as I love, I rebuke and chasten.

00:15:05.613 --> 00:15:08.033
Be zealous therefore, and repent.

00:15:09.253 --> 00:15:12.253
Behold, I stand at the door and knock.

00:15:12.713 --> 00:15:19.053
If any man hear my voice and open the door, I will come in to them, and will sup with

00:15:19.053 --> 00:15:21.173
him, and he with me.

00:15:21.633 --> 00:15:28.573
To him that overcometh, will I grant to sit with me in my throne, even as I also overcame,

00:15:29.053 --> 00:15:32.153
and am set down with my father in his throne.

00:15:32.813 --> 00:15:38.353
He that hath an ear, let him hear what the Spirit saith unto the churches.

00:15:39.913 --> 00:15:41.873
The

00:16:03.379 --> 00:16:10.089
After this I looked, and behold, a door was opened in heaven, and the first voice which

00:16:10.089 --> 00:16:17.389
I heard was as it were of a trumpet talking with me, which said, Come up hither, and I

00:16:17.389 --> 00:16:24.189
will shew thee things which must be hereafter. And immediately I was in the spirit, and behold,

00:16:24.529 --> 00:16:31.409
a throne was set in heaven, and one sat on the throne, and he that sat was to look upon

00:16:31.409 --> 00:16:37.769
like a jasper and a sardine stone, and there was a rainbow round about the throne, in sight

00:16:37.769 --> 00:16:44.349
like unto an emerald, and round about the throne were four and twenty seats, and upon

00:16:44.349 --> 00:16:50.389
the seats I saw four and twenty elders sitting, clothed in white raiment, and they had on

00:16:50.389 --> 00:16:56.109
their heads crowns of gold. And out of the throne proceeded lightnings and thunderings

00:16:56.109 --> 00:17:01.689
and voices, and there were seven lamps of fire burning before the throne, which are

00:17:01.689 --> 00:17:09.009
of God. And before the throne there was a sea of glass like unto crystal, and in the

00:17:09.009 --> 00:17:15.689
midst of the throne and round about the throne were four beasts full of eyes before and behind,

00:17:16.129 --> 00:17:22.789
and the first beast was like a lion, and the second beast like a calf, and the third beast

00:17:22.789 --> 00:17:29.969
had a face as a man, and the fourth beast was like a flying eagle, and the four beasts

00:17:29.969 --> 00:17:35.969
had each of them six wings about him, and they were full of eyes within, and they rest

00:17:35.969 --> 00:17:44.329
not day and night, saying, Holy, holy, holy Lord God Almighty, which was and is and is

00:17:44.329 --> 00:17:50.529
to come! And when those beasts give glory and honour and thanks to him that sat on the

00:17:50.529 --> 00:17:56.169
throne, who liveth for ever and ever, the four and twenty elders fall down before him

00:17:56.169 --> 00:18:02.529
that sat on the throne, and worship him that liveth for ever and ever, and cast their crowns

00:18:02.529 --> 00:18:08.889
before the throne, saying, Thou art worthy, O Lord, to receive glory and honour and power,

00:18:09.269 --> 00:18:14.949
for thou hast created all things, and for thy pleasure they are and were created.

00:18:14.949 --> 00:18:18.189
The

00:18:39.608 --> 00:18:45.648
And I saw in the right hand of him that sat on the throne a book written within and on

00:18:45.648 --> 00:18:48.248
the back side, sealed with seven seals.

00:18:48.808 --> 00:18:52.788
And I saw a strong angel proclaiming with a loud voice,

00:18:53.548 --> 00:18:57.728
Who is worthy to open the book and to loose the seals thereof?

00:18:58.568 --> 00:19:05.368
And no man in heaven, nor in earth, nor under the earth, was able to open the book, neither to look

00:19:05.368 --> 00:19:12.688
thereon. And I wept much, because no man was found worthy to open and to read the book, neither to

00:19:12.688 --> 00:19:21.388
look thereon. And one of the elders saith unto me, Weep not, behold, the lion of the tribe of Judah,

00:19:21.668 --> 00:19:27.128
the root of David, hath prevailed to open the book and to loose the seven seals thereof.

00:19:27.688 --> 00:19:34.208
And I beheld, and lo, in the midst of the throne and of the four beasts, and in the midst of the

00:19:34.208 --> 00:19:42.548
elders, stood a lamb as it had been slain, having seven horns and seven eyes, which are the seven

00:19:42.548 --> 00:19:48.388
spirits of God sent forth into all the earth. And he came and took the book out of the right hand of

00:19:48.388 --> 00:19:54.188
him that sat upon the throne. And when he had taken the book, the four beasts and the four and

00:19:54.188 --> 00:20:00.288
twenty elders fell down before the lamb, having every one of them harps and golden vials full of

00:20:00.288 --> 00:20:08.208
odours, which are the prayers of saints. And they sung a new song, saying, Thou art worthy to take

00:20:08.208 --> 00:20:15.008
the book and to open the seals thereof. For thou wast slain, and hast redeemed us to God by thy

00:20:15.008 --> 00:20:21.908
blood out of every kindred and tongue and people and nation, and hast made us unto our God kings

00:20:21.908 --> 00:20:28.768
and priests, and we shall reign on the earth. And I beheld, and I heard the voice of many angels

00:20:28.768 --> 00:20:35.548
round about the throne and the beasts and the elders, and the number of them was ten thousand

00:20:35.548 --> 00:20:43.588
times ten thousand, and thousands of thousands, saying with a loud voice, Worthy is the lamb that

00:20:43.588 --> 00:20:50.328
was slain to receive power and riches and wisdom and strength and honour and glory and blessing,

00:20:51.088 --> 00:20:57.408
and every creature which is in heaven and on the earth and under the earth, and such as are in the

00:20:57.408 --> 00:21:05.008
sea and all that are in them, heard I saying, Blessing and honour and glory and power be unto

00:21:05.008 --> 00:21:12.488
him that sitteth upon the throne and unto the Lamb for ever and ever. And the four beasts said,

00:21:12.928 --> 00:21:20.568
Amen. And the four and twenty elders fell down and worshipped him that liveth for ever and ever.

00:21:21.888 --> 00:21:24.028
The

00:21:45.368 --> 00:21:50.448
And I saw when the Lamb opened one of the seals, and I heard as it were the noise of

00:21:50.448 --> 00:21:55.288
thunder one of the four beasts saying, Come and see!

00:21:55.288 --> 00:22:02.468
And I saw, and behold, a white horse, and he that sat on him had a bow, and a crown

00:22:02.468 --> 00:22:06.548
was given unto him, and he went forth conquering and to conquer.

00:22:07.048 --> 00:22:13.608
And when he had opened the second seal, I heard the second beast say, Come and see!

00:22:14.188 --> 00:22:19.448
And there went out another horse that was red, and power was given to him that sat thereon

00:22:19.448 --> 00:22:23.628
to take peace from the earth, and that they should kill one another.

00:22:24.178 --> 00:22:27.028
And there was given unto him a great sword.

00:22:27.948 --> 00:22:33.908
And when he had opened the third seal, I heard the third beast say, Come and see!

00:22:34.308 --> 00:22:40.988
And I beheld, and lo, a black horse, and he that sat on him had a pair of balances in

00:22:40.988 --> 00:22:41.648
his hand.

00:22:42.268 --> 00:22:48.088
And I heard a voice in the midst of the four beasts say, A measure of wheat for a penny,

00:22:48.088 --> 00:22:54.108
and three measures of barley for a penny, and see thou hurt not the oil and the wine.

00:22:54.908 --> 00:23:00.568
And when he had opened the fourth seal, I heard the voice of the fourth beast say, Come

00:23:00.568 --> 00:23:01.408
and see!

00:23:01.928 --> 00:23:09.388
And I looked, and behold, a pale horse, and his name that sat on him was Death, and Hell

00:23:09.388 --> 00:23:14.988
followed with him, and power was given unto them over the fourth part of the earth to

00:23:14.988 --> 00:23:20.268
kill with sword, and with hunger, and with death, and with the beasts of the earth.

00:23:21.008 --> 00:23:26.668
And when he had opened the fifth seal, I saw under the altar the souls of them that were

00:23:26.668 --> 00:23:30.608
slain for the word of God, and for the testimony which they held.

00:23:31.208 --> 00:23:37.648
And they cried with a loud voice, saying, How long, O Lord, holy and true dost thou

00:23:37.648 --> 00:23:41.128
not judge and avenge our blood on them that dwell on the earth?

00:23:41.708 --> 00:23:46.828
And white robes were given unto every one of them, and it was said unto them that they

00:23:46.828 --> 00:23:51.868
should rest yet for a little season, until their fellow-servants also, and their brethren

00:23:51.868 --> 00:23:55.048
that should be killed as they were, should be fulfilled.

00:23:55.888 --> 00:24:01.848
And I beheld when he had opened the sixth seal, and lo, there was a great earthquake,

00:24:02.228 --> 00:24:08.268
and the sun became black as sackcloth of hair, and the moon became as blood, and the stars

00:24:08.268 --> 00:24:14.048
of heaven fell unto the earth, even as a fig-tree casteth her untimely figs when she is shaken

00:24:14.048 --> 00:24:19.568
of a mighty wind, and the heaven departed as a scroll when it is rolled together, and

00:24:19.568 --> 00:24:22.788
every mountain and island were moved out of their places.

00:24:23.448 --> 00:24:28.708
And the kings of the earth, and the great men, and the rich men, and the chief captains,

00:24:28.868 --> 00:24:34.008
and the mighty men, and every bondman, and every freeman, hid themselves in the dens

00:24:34.008 --> 00:24:40.168
and in the rocks of the mountains, and said to the mountains and rocks, Foul on us, and

00:24:40.168 --> 00:24:44.968
hide us from the face of him that sitteth on the throne, and from the wrath of the Lamb,

00:24:45.348 --> 00:24:50.348
for the great day of his wrath is come, and who shall be able to stand?

00:25:16.075 --> 00:25:21.595
And after these things I saw four angels standing on the four corners of the earth, holding

00:25:21.595 --> 00:25:26.815
the four winds of the earth, that the wind should not blow on the earth nor on the sea

00:25:26.815 --> 00:25:28.315
nor on any tree.

00:25:28.955 --> 00:25:34.355
And I saw another angel ascending from the east, having the seal of the living God.

00:25:34.815 --> 00:25:40.215
And he cried with a loud voice to the four angels, to whom it was given to hurt the earth

00:25:40.215 --> 00:25:47.175
and the sea, saying, Hurt not the earth, neither the sea nor the trees, till we have sealed

00:25:47.175 --> 00:25:49.775
the servants of our God in their foreheads.

00:25:50.575 --> 00:25:53.535
And I heard the number of them which were sealed.

00:25:53.895 --> 00:25:58.995
And there were sealed an hundred and forty and four thousand of all the tribes of the

00:25:58.995 --> 00:26:00.195
children of Israel.

00:26:00.975 --> 00:26:04.435
Of the tribe of Judah were sealed 12,000.

00:26:04.775 --> 00:26:08.135
Of the tribe of Reuben were sealed 12,000.

00:26:08.475 --> 00:26:11.655
Of the tribe of Gad were sealed 12,000.

00:26:11.895 --> 00:26:15.255
Of the tribe of Assur were sealed 12,000.

00:26:15.575 --> 00:26:18.955
Of the tribe of Nephtilim were sealed 12,000.

00:26:18.955 --> 00:26:26.255
the tribe of Manassees were sealed 12,000, of the tribe of Simeon were sealed 12,000,

00:26:26.515 --> 00:26:33.595
of the tribe of Levi were sealed 12,000, of the tribe of Issachar were sealed 12,000,

00:26:33.895 --> 00:26:40.755
of the tribe of Zabulon were sealed 12,000, of the tribe of Joseph were sealed 12,000,

00:26:40.755 --> 00:26:45.035
of the tribe of Benjamin were sealed 12,000.

00:26:45.935 --> 00:26:51.475
After this I beheld, and lo, a great multitude which no man could number,

00:26:51.635 --> 00:26:56.875
of all nations and kindreds and people and tongues, stood before the throne,

00:26:57.135 --> 00:27:01.555
and before the Lamb, clothed with white robes and palms in their hands,

00:27:01.835 --> 00:27:04.435
and cried with a loud voice, saying,

00:27:05.295 --> 00:27:09.975
Salvation to our God which sitteth upon the throne and unto the Lamb!

00:27:10.555 --> 00:27:16.255
And all the angels stood round about the throne and about the elders and the four beasts,

00:27:16.635 --> 00:27:21.555
and fell before the throne on their faces, and worshipped God, saying,

00:27:22.195 --> 00:27:33.335
Amen! Blessing and glory and wisdom and thanksgiving and honour and power and might be unto our God for ever and ever! Amen!

00:27:34.055 --> 00:27:37.195
And one of the elders answered, saying unto me,

00:27:37.975 --> 00:27:42.475
What are these which are arrayed in white robes, and whence came they?

00:27:43.055 --> 00:27:44.595
And I said unto him,

00:27:45.035 --> 00:27:46.935
Sir, thou knowest?

00:27:47.335 --> 00:27:48.555
And he said to me,

00:27:49.035 --> 00:27:56.555
These are they which came out of great tribulation and have washed their robes and made them white in the blood of the Lamb.

00:27:56.975 --> 00:28:02.315
Therefore are they before the throne of God and serve Him day and night in His temple,

00:28:02.615 --> 00:28:06.095
and He that sitteth on the throne shall dwell among them.

00:28:06.095 --> 00:28:13.455
They shall hunger no more, neither thirst any more, neither shall the sun light on them, nor any heat.

00:28:13.935 --> 00:28:20.155
For the Lamb which is in the midst of the throne shall feed them and shall lead them unto living fountains of waters,

00:28:20.415 --> 00:28:24.235
and God shall wipe away all tears from their eyes.

00:28:25.395 --> 00:28:27.615
The

00:28:46.822 --> 00:28:54.862
VIII. And when he had opened the seventh seal, there was silence in heaven about the space

00:28:54.862 --> 00:28:56.442
of half an hour.

00:28:58.022 --> 00:29:04.422
And I saw the seven angels which stood before God, and to them were given seven trumpets.

00:29:04.782 --> 00:29:11.262
And another angel came and stood at the altar, having a golden censer, and there was given unto

00:29:11.262 --> 00:29:17.602
him much incense that he should offer it with the prayers of all saints, upon the golden altar which

00:29:17.602 --> 00:29:22.962
was before the throne. And the smoke of the incense which came with the prayers of the saints

00:29:22.962 --> 00:29:29.622
ascended up before God out of the angel's hand. And the angel took the censer and filled it with

00:29:29.622 --> 00:29:35.682
fire of the altar and cast it into the earth. And there were voices and thunderings and

00:29:35.682 --> 00:29:41.842
lightnings and an earthquake. And the seven angels which had the seven trumpets prepared

00:29:41.842 --> 00:29:49.202
themselves to sound. The first angel sounded, and there followed hail and fire mingled with blood,

00:29:49.202 --> 00:29:55.842
and they were cast upon the earth. And the third part of trees was burnt up, and all green grass

00:29:55.842 --> 00:30:03.042
was burnt up. And the second angel sounded. And as it were a great mountain burning with fire was

00:30:03.042 --> 00:30:09.462
cast into the sea, and the third part of the sea became blood. And the third part of the creatures

00:30:09.462 --> 00:30:16.062
which were in the sea and had life died. And the third part of the ships were destroyed. And the

00:30:16.062 --> 00:30:22.502
third angel sounded. And there fell a great star from heaven burning as it were a lamp. And it fell

00:30:22.502 --> 00:30:28.842
upon the third part of the rivers and upon the fountains of waters. And the name of the star is

00:30:28.842 --> 00:30:36.162
called Wormwood. And the third part of the waters became Wormwood. And many men died of the waters

00:30:36.162 --> 00:30:41.902
because they were made bitter. And the fourth angel sounded. And the third part of the sun was

00:30:41.902 --> 00:30:47.942
smitten, and the third part of the moon, and the third part of the stars. So as the third part of

00:30:47.942 --> 00:30:54.502
them was darkened, and the day shone not for a third part of it, and the night likewise. And I

00:30:54.502 --> 00:30:59.882
beheld and heard an angel flying through the midst of heaven, saying with a loud voice,

00:31:01.202 --> 00:31:06.982
Woe, woe, woe to the inhabiters of the earth by reason of the other voices of the trumpet of

00:31:06.982 --> 00:31:13.342
three angels which are yet to sound. The

00:31:19.183 --> 00:31:40.783
9. And the fifth angel sounded, and I saw a star fall from heaven unto the earth, and

00:31:40.783 --> 00:31:46.843
to him was given the key of the bottomless pit. And he opened the bottomless pit, and

00:31:46.843 --> 00:31:52.463
there arose a smoke out of the pit, as the smoke of a great furnace. And the sun and

00:31:52.463 --> 00:31:58.183
the air were darkened by reason of the smoke of the pit. And there came out of the smoke

00:31:58.183 --> 00:32:03.943
locusts upon the earth, and unto them was given power, as the scorpions of the earth

00:32:03.943 --> 00:32:09.263
have power. And it was commanded them that they should not hurt the grass of the earth,

00:32:09.443 --> 00:32:15.083
neither any green thing, neither any tree, but only those men which have not the seal

00:32:15.083 --> 00:32:20.563
in their foreheads. And to them it was given that they should not kill them, but that they

00:32:20.563 --> 00:32:26.083
should be tormented five months. And their torment was as the torment of a scorpion when

00:32:26.083 --> 00:32:32.603
he striketh a man. And in those days shall men seek death, and shall not find it, and

00:32:32.603 --> 00:32:38.443
shall desire to die, and death shall flee from them. And the shapes of the locusts were

00:32:38.443 --> 00:32:43.723
like unto horses prepared unto battle, and on their heads were, as it were, crowns like

00:32:43.723 --> 00:32:49.603
gold, and their faces were as the faces of men. And they had hair as the hair of women,

00:32:49.763 --> 00:32:55.383
and their teeth were as the teeth of lions. And they had breastplates, as it were breastplates

00:32:55.383 --> 00:33:00.583
of iron. And the sound of their wings was as the sound of chariots of many horses running

00:33:00.583 --> 00:33:07.003
to battle. And they had tails like unto scorpions, and there were stings in their tails, and

00:33:07.003 --> 00:33:13.103
their power was to hurt men five months. And they had a king over them, which is the angel

00:33:13.103 --> 00:33:19.343
of the bottomless pit, whose name in the Hebrew tongue is Abaddon, but in the Greek tongue

00:33:19.343 --> 00:33:27.383
hath his name Apollyon. One woe is past, and behold, there come two woes more hereafter.

00:33:28.043 --> 00:33:32.843
And the sixth angel sounded, and I heard a voice from the four horns of the golden altar

00:33:32.843 --> 00:33:39.583
which is before God saying to the sixth angel which had the trumpet, Loose the four angels

00:33:39.583 --> 00:33:45.063
which are bound in the great river Euphrates. And the four angels were loosed, which were

00:33:45.063 --> 00:33:51.163
prepared for an hour, and a day, and a month, and a year, for to slay the third part of

00:33:51.163 --> 00:33:59.283
men. And the number of the army of the horsemen were two hundred thousand thousand. And I

00:33:59.283 --> 00:34:04.623
heard the number of them. And thus I saw the horses in the vision, and them that sat on

00:34:04.623 --> 00:34:10.523
them, having breastplates of fire, and of jacinth, and brimstone. And the heads of the

00:34:10.523 --> 00:34:15.663
horses were as the heads of lions, and out of their mouths issued fire, and smoke, and

00:34:15.663 --> 00:34:21.803
brimstone. By these three was the third part of men killed, by the fire, and by the smoke,

00:34:21.923 --> 00:34:27.263
and by the brimstone which issued out of their mouths. For their power is in their mouth,

00:34:27.343 --> 00:34:32.823
and in their tails. For their tails were like unto serpents, and had heads, and with

00:34:32.823 --> 00:34:38.243
them they do hurt. And the rest of the men which were not killed by these plagues, yet

00:34:38.243 --> 00:34:42.723
repented not of the works of their hands, that they should not worship doubles, and

00:34:42.723 --> 00:34:48.283
idols of gold, and silver, and brass, and stone, and of wood, which neither can see,

00:34:48.503 --> 00:34:54.123
nor hear, nor walk. Neither repented they of their murders, nor of their sorceries,

00:34:54.263 --> 00:34:58.683
nor of their fornication, nor of their thefts.

00:35:22.246 --> 00:35:28.026
And I saw another mighty angel come down from heaven, clothed with a cloud, and a rainbow

00:35:28.026 --> 00:35:33.706
was upon his head, and his face was as it were the sun, and his feet as pillars of fire.

00:35:34.266 --> 00:35:41.266
And he had in his hand a little book, open, and he set his right foot upon the sea, and his left

00:35:41.266 --> 00:35:47.786
foot on the earth, and cried with a loud voice, as when a lion roareth, and when he had cried,

00:35:48.266 --> 00:35:53.146
seven thunders uttered their voices. And when the seven thunders had uttered their voices,

00:35:53.326 --> 00:35:58.066
I was about to write, and I heard a voice from heaven saying unto me,

00:35:58.646 --> 00:36:03.846
Seal up those things which the seven thunders uttered, and write them not.

00:36:04.606 --> 00:36:10.066
And the angel which I saw stand upon the sea and upon the earth lifted up his hand to heaven,

00:36:10.606 --> 00:36:16.306
and swear by him that liveth for ever and ever, who created heaven and the things that therein are,

00:36:16.426 --> 00:36:21.286
and the earth and the things that therein are, and the sea and the things which are therein,

00:36:21.626 --> 00:36:27.346
that there should be time no longer, but in the days of the voice of the seventh angel,

00:36:27.346 --> 00:36:33.146
when he shall begin to sound, the mystery of God should be finished as he hath declared to

00:36:33.146 --> 00:36:39.746
his servants the prophets. And the voice which I heard from heaven spake unto me again, and said,

00:36:40.566 --> 00:36:46.646
Go and take the little book which is open in the hand of the angel, which standeth upon the sea

00:36:46.646 --> 00:36:53.786
and upon the earth. And I went unto the angel, and said unto him, Give me the little book.

00:36:53.786 --> 00:37:00.066
And he said unto me, Take it and eat it up, and it shall make thy belly bitter,

00:37:00.386 --> 00:37:07.246
but it shall be in thy mouth sweet as honey. And I took the little book out of the angel's hand

00:37:07.246 --> 00:37:14.326
and ate it up, and it was in my mouth sweet as honey, and as soon as I had eaten it my belly

00:37:14.326 --> 00:37:21.886
was bitter. And he said unto me, Thou must prophesy again before many peoples and nations

00:37:21.886 --> 00:37:28.266
and tongues and kings. The

00:37:34.476 --> 00:37:35.036
11.

00:37:49.016 --> 00:37:55.776
And there was given me a reed like unto a rod, and the angel stood, saying, Rise and

00:37:55.776 --> 00:38:00.036
measure the temple of God, and the altar, and them that worship therein.

00:38:00.396 --> 00:38:05.816
But the court which is without the temple leave out, and measure it not, for it is given

00:38:05.816 --> 00:38:11.256
unto the Gentiles, and the holy city shall they tread underfoot forty and two months.

00:38:11.656 --> 00:38:17.216
And I will give power unto my two witnesses, and they shall prophesy a thousand two hundred

00:38:17.216 --> 00:38:20.636
and three score days, clothed in sackcloth.

00:38:20.856 --> 00:38:26.176
These are the two olive trees, and the two candlesticks, standing before the God of the

00:38:26.176 --> 00:38:26.476
earth.

00:38:27.016 --> 00:38:33.076
And if any man will hurt them, fire proceedeth out of their mouth, and devoureth their enemies.

00:38:33.556 --> 00:38:37.456
And if any man will hurt them, he must in this manner be killed.

00:38:38.116 --> 00:38:43.436
These have power to shut heaven that it reign not in the days of their prophecy, and have

00:38:43.436 --> 00:38:48.976
power over waters to turn them to blood, and to smite the earth with all plagues as often

00:38:48.976 --> 00:38:49.836
as they will.

00:38:50.416 --> 00:38:55.496
And when they shall have finished their testimony, the beast that ascendeth out of the bottomless

00:38:55.496 --> 00:38:59.656
pit shall make war against them, and shall overcome them and kill them.

00:39:00.296 --> 00:39:05.656
And their dead bodies shall lie in the street of the great city which spiritually is called

00:39:05.656 --> 00:39:09.376
Sodom and Egypt, where also our Lord was crucified.

00:39:09.956 --> 00:39:15.556
And they of the people and kindreds and tongues and nations shall see their dead bodies three

00:39:15.556 --> 00:39:20.296
days and an half, and shall not suffer their dead bodies to be put in graves.

00:39:20.696 --> 00:39:25.876
And they that dwell upon the earth shall rejoice over them, and make merry, and shall send

00:39:25.876 --> 00:39:31.396
gifts one to another, because these two prophets tormented them that dwelt on the earth.

00:39:31.996 --> 00:39:37.356
And after three days and an half the spirit of life from God entered into them, and they

00:39:37.356 --> 00:39:41.476
stood upon their feet, and great fear fell upon them which saw them.

00:39:41.676 --> 00:39:46.936
And they heard a great voice from heaven saying unto them, Come up hither!

00:39:47.376 --> 00:39:51.956
And they ascended up to heaven in a cloud, and their enemies beheld them.

00:39:52.396 --> 00:39:57.996
And the same hour was there a great earthquake, and the tenth part of the city fell, and in

00:39:57.996 --> 00:40:04.036
the earthquake were slain of men seven thousand, and the remnant were affrighted and gave glory

00:40:04.036 --> 00:40:05.256
to the God of heaven.

00:40:06.156 --> 00:40:10.916
The second woe is past, and behold the third woe cometh quickly.

00:40:11.576 --> 00:40:17.216
And the seventh angel sounded, and there were great voices in heaven saying, The kingdoms

00:40:17.216 --> 00:40:22.636
of this world are become the kingdoms of our Lord and of his Christ, and he shall reign

00:40:22.636 --> 00:40:24.136
for ever and ever.

00:40:24.636 --> 00:40:30.256
And the four and twenty elders which sat before God on their seats fell upon their faces and

00:40:30.256 --> 00:40:36.876
worshipped God, saying, We give thee thanks, O Lord God Almighty, which art and wast and

00:40:36.876 --> 00:40:42.096
art to come, because thou hast taken to thee thy great power and hast reigned.

00:40:42.316 --> 00:40:47.216
And the nations were angry, and thy wrath is come, and the time of the dead that they

00:40:47.216 --> 00:40:51.856
should be judged, and that thou shouldest give reward unto thy servants the prophets,

00:40:52.156 --> 00:40:57.596
and to the saints, and them that fear thy name, small and great, and shouldest destroy

00:40:57.596 --> 00:40:59.376
them which destroy the earth.

00:40:59.876 --> 00:41:04.836
And the temple of God was opened in heaven, and there was seen in his temple the ark of

00:41:04.836 --> 00:41:09.996
his testament, and there were lightnings, and voices, and thunderings, and an earthquake,

00:41:10.456 --> 00:41:11.776
and great hail.

00:41:13.396 --> 00:41:15.296
The

00:41:33.253 --> 00:41:37.893
And there appeared a great wonder in heaven,

00:41:38.173 --> 00:41:43.693
a woman clothed with the sun and the moon under her feet, and upon her head a crown

00:41:43.693 --> 00:41:49.893
of twelve stars, and she being with child cried, travailing in birth and pained to

00:41:49.893 --> 00:41:56.333
be delivered. And there appeared another wonder in heaven, and behold, a great red dragon,

00:41:56.653 --> 00:42:02.813
having seven heads and ten horns, and seven crowns upon his heads. And his tail drew the

00:42:02.813 --> 00:42:08.253
third part of the stars of heaven, and did cast them to the earth. And the dragon stood

00:42:08.253 --> 00:42:13.673
before the woman which was ready to be delivered, for to devour her child as soon as it was

00:42:13.673 --> 00:42:19.173
born. And she brought forth a man-child who was to rule all nations with a rod of iron.

00:42:19.533 --> 00:42:25.893
And her child was caught up unto God and to his throne. And the woman fled into the wilderness

00:42:25.893 --> 00:42:31.093
where she hath a place prepared of God that they should feed her there a thousand, two

00:42:31.093 --> 00:42:37.093
hundred, and three score days. And there was war in heaven. Michael and his angels fought

00:42:37.093 --> 00:42:42.633
against the dragon, and the dragon fought and his angels, and prevailed not. Neither

00:42:42.633 --> 00:42:48.353
was their place found any more in heaven. And the great dragon was cast out, that old

00:42:48.353 --> 00:42:53.933
serpent called the Devil and Satan, which deceiveth the whole world. He was cast out

00:42:53.933 --> 00:42:59.553
into the earth, and his angels were cast out with him. And I heard a loud voice saying

00:42:59.553 --> 00:43:05.913
in heaven, Now is come salvation and strength, and the kingdom of our God, and the power

00:43:05.913 --> 00:43:11.873
of his Christ. For the accuser of our brethren is cast down, which accused them before our

00:43:11.873 --> 00:43:17.213
God day and night. And they overcame him by the blood of the lamb, and by the word

00:43:17.213 --> 00:43:23.213
of their testimony, and they loved not their lives unto the death. Therefore rejoice, ye

00:43:23.213 --> 00:43:28.373
heavens, and ye that dwell in them. Woe to the inhabiters of the earth and of the sea!

00:43:28.713 --> 00:43:33.753
For the devil is come down unto you, having great wrath, because he knoweth that he hath

00:43:33.753 --> 00:43:40.133
but a short time. And when the dragon saw that he was cast unto the earth, he persecuted

00:43:40.133 --> 00:43:45.153
the woman which brought forth the man-child. And to the woman were given two wings of a

00:43:45.153 --> 00:43:50.233
great eagle, that she might fly into the wilderness, into her place where she is nourished for

00:43:50.233 --> 00:43:56.133
a time, and times, and half a time, from the face of the serpent. And the serpent cast

00:43:56.133 --> 00:44:00.753
out of his mouth water as a flood after the woman, that he might cause her to be carried

00:44:00.753 --> 00:44:05.913
away of the flood. And the earth helped the woman, and the earth opened her mouth and

00:44:05.913 --> 00:44:11.053
swallowed up the flood which the dragon cast out of his mouth. And the dragon was wroth

00:44:11.053 --> 00:44:16.053
with the woman, and went to make war with a remnant of her seed, which keep the commandments

00:44:16.053 --> 00:44:19.453
of God, and have the testimony of Jesus Christ.

00:44:43.116 --> 00:44:48.696
And I stood upon the sand of the sea, and saw a beast rise up out of the sea, having

00:44:48.696 --> 00:44:55.296
seven heads and ten horns, and upon his horns ten crowns, and upon his heads the name of

00:44:55.296 --> 00:45:01.816
And the beast, which I saw, was like unto a leopard, and his feet were as the feet of

00:45:01.816 --> 00:45:07.616
a bear, and his mouth as the mouth of a lion, and the dragon gave him his power, and his

00:45:07.616 --> 00:45:09.176
seat and great authority.

00:45:09.556 --> 00:45:15.356
And I saw one of his heads, as it were wounded to death, and his deadly wound was healed,

00:45:15.616 --> 00:45:18.256
and all the world wondered after the beast.

00:45:18.756 --> 00:45:23.436
And they worshipped the dragon which gave power unto the beast, and they worshipped

00:45:23.436 --> 00:45:29.856
the beast, saying, Who is like unto the beast, who is able to make war with him?

00:45:30.496 --> 00:45:36.616
And there was given unto him a mouth speaking great things and blasphemies, and power was

00:45:36.616 --> 00:45:39.916
given unto him to continue forty and two months.

00:45:40.676 --> 00:45:46.536
And he opened his mouth in blasphemy against God, to blaspheme his name and his tabernacle

00:45:46.536 --> 00:45:48.276
and them that dwell in heaven.

00:45:48.836 --> 00:45:53.936
And it was given unto him to make war with the saints and to overcome them, and power

00:45:53.936 --> 00:45:57.996
was given him over all kindreds and tongues and nations.

00:45:58.316 --> 00:46:03.456
And all that dwell upon the earth shall worship him, whose names are not written in the book

00:46:03.456 --> 00:46:07.136
of life of the Lamb slain from the foundation of the world.

00:46:07.536 --> 00:46:10.756
If any man have an ear, let him hear.

00:46:11.456 --> 00:46:15.236
He that leadeth into captivity shall go into captivity.

00:46:15.616 --> 00:46:19.316
He that killeth with the sword must be killed with the sword.

00:46:19.996 --> 00:46:23.056
Here is the patience and the faith of the saints.

00:46:24.196 --> 00:46:29.256
And I beheld another beast coming up out of the earth, and he had two horns like a lamb,

00:46:29.556 --> 00:46:35.496
and he spake as a dragon, and he exerciseth all the power of the first beast before him,

00:46:35.876 --> 00:46:41.376
and causeth the earth and them which dwell therein to worship the first beast whose deadly

00:46:41.376 --> 00:46:42.436
wound was healed.

00:46:42.876 --> 00:46:47.776
And he doeth great wonders, so that he maketh fire come down from heaven on the earth in

00:46:47.776 --> 00:46:52.796
the sight of men, and deceiveth them that dwell on the earth by the means of those miracles,

00:46:53.076 --> 00:46:58.176
which he had power to do in the sight of the beast, saying to them that dwell on the earth,

00:46:58.316 --> 00:47:03.736
that they should make an image to the beast which had the wound by a sword and did live.

00:47:03.916 --> 00:47:08.716
And he had power to give life unto the image of the beast, that the image of the beast

00:47:08.716 --> 00:47:13.376
should both speak, and cause that as many as would not worship the image of the beast

00:47:13.376 --> 00:47:14.656
should be killed.

00:47:15.256 --> 00:47:21.496
And he causeth all, both small and great, rich and poor, free and bond, to receive a

00:47:21.496 --> 00:47:27.496
mark in their right hand or in their foreheads, and that no man might buy or sell save he

00:47:27.496 --> 00:47:31.736
that had the mark, or the name of the beast, or the number of his name.

00:47:32.616 --> 00:47:33.816
Here is wisdom.

00:47:34.196 --> 00:47:38.056
Let him that hath understanding count the number of the beast.

00:47:38.056 --> 00:47:46.716
For it is the number of a man, and his number is six hundred threescore and six.

00:48:12.478 --> 00:48:18.418
And I looked, and lo, a lamb stood on the Mount Sion, and with him an hundred forty

00:48:18.418 --> 00:48:22.878
and four thousand having his father's name written in their foreheads.

00:48:22.878 --> 00:48:28.358
And I heard a voice from heaven as the voice of many waters, and as the voice of a great thunder,

00:48:28.618 --> 00:48:33.398
and I heard the voice of harpers harping with their harps. And they sung, as it were,

00:48:33.638 --> 00:48:39.518
a new song before the throne, and before the four beasts, and the elders. And no man could learn

00:48:39.518 --> 00:48:44.058
that song but the hundred and forty and four thousand which were redeemed from the earth.

00:48:44.738 --> 00:48:49.898
These are they which were not defiled with women, for they are virgins. These are they

00:48:49.898 --> 00:48:55.058
which follow the Lamb whithersoever he goeth. These were redeemed from among men,

00:48:55.198 --> 00:49:01.258
being the firstfruits unto God and to the Lamb. And in their mouth was found no guile,

00:49:01.418 --> 00:49:07.418
for they are without fault before the throne of God. And I saw another angel fly in the midst of

00:49:07.418 --> 00:49:12.478
heaven, having the everlasting gospel to preach unto them that dwell on the earth, and to every

00:49:12.478 --> 00:49:17.398
nation, and kindred, and tongue, and people, saying with a loud voice,

00:49:18.098 --> 00:49:25.278
Fair God, and give glory to him, for the hour of his judgment is come, and worship him that made

00:49:25.278 --> 00:49:31.978
heaven, and earth, and the sea, and the fountains of waters. And there followed another angel,

00:49:32.318 --> 00:49:39.718
saying, Babylon is fallen, is fallen, that great city, because she made all nations drink of the

00:49:39.718 --> 00:49:46.118
wrath of her fornication. And the third angel followed them, saying with a loud voice,

00:49:46.658 --> 00:49:53.018
If any man worship the beast and his image, and receive his mark in his forehead or in his hand,

00:49:53.338 --> 00:49:57.858
the same shall drink of the wine of the wrath of God which is poured out without mixture

00:49:57.858 --> 00:50:04.298
into the cup of his indignation. And he shall be tormented with fire and brimstone in the presence

00:50:04.298 --> 00:50:10.418
of the holy angels and in the presence of the lamb. And the smoke of their torment ascendeth

00:50:10.418 --> 00:50:16.778
up for ever and ever. And they have no rest day nor night who worship the beast and his image,

00:50:16.978 --> 00:50:23.278
and whosoever receiveth the mark of his name. Here is the patience of the saints. Here are

00:50:23.278 --> 00:50:28.998
they that keep the commandments of God and the faith of Jesus. And I heard a voice from heaven

00:50:28.998 --> 00:50:35.198
saying unto me, Right, blessed are the dead which die in the Lord from henceforth.

00:50:35.738 --> 00:50:41.438
Yea, saith the Spirit, that they may rest from their labours, and their works do follow them.

00:50:42.318 --> 00:50:49.478
And I looked, and behold a white cloud, and upon the cloud one sat like unto the Son of Man,

00:50:49.678 --> 00:50:56.398
having on his head a golden crown, and in his hand a sharp sickle. And another angel came out

00:50:56.398 --> 00:51:03.638
the temple, crying with a loud voice to him that sat on the cloud, Thrust in thy sickle and reap,

00:51:03.958 --> 00:51:10.318
for the time is come for thee to reap, for the harvest of the earth is ripe. And he that sat

00:51:10.318 --> 00:51:16.498
on the cloud thrust in his sickle on the earth, and the earth was reaped. And another angel came

00:51:16.498 --> 00:51:22.178
out of the temple which is in heaven, he also having a sharp sickle. And another angel came

00:51:22.178 --> 00:51:27.658
out from the altar which had power over fire, and cried with a loud cry to him that had the

00:51:27.658 --> 00:51:34.838
sharp sickle, saying, Thrust in thy sharp sickle, and gather the clusters of the vine of the earth,

00:51:35.098 --> 00:51:41.598
for her grapes are fully ripe. And the angel thrust in his sickle into the earth, and gathered the

00:51:41.598 --> 00:51:47.718
vine of the earth, and cast it into the great winepress of the wrath of God. And the winepress was

00:51:47.718 --> 00:51:51.498
trodden without the city, and blood came out of the winepress,

00:51:51.718 --> 00:51:57.798
even unto the horse-bridles, by the space of a thousand and six hundred fur-lawns.

00:51:59.298 --> 00:52:01.098
The

00:52:07.203 --> 00:52:07.803
15.

00:52:22.203 --> 00:52:28.043
And I saw another sign in heaven, great and marvellous, seven angels having the seven

00:52:28.043 --> 00:52:32.103
last plagues, for in them is filled up the wrath of God.

00:52:32.643 --> 00:52:38.923
And I saw, as it were, a sea of glass mingled with fire, and them that had gotten the victory

00:52:38.923 --> 00:52:43.823
over the beast, and over his image, and over his mark, and over the number of his name,

00:52:44.343 --> 00:52:47.663
stand on the sea of glass, having the harps of God.

00:52:47.863 --> 00:52:53.183
And they sing the song of Moses, the servant of God, and the song of the Lamb, saying,

00:52:53.183 --> 00:52:59.083
Great and marvellous are thy works, Lord God Almighty!

00:52:59.823 --> 00:53:03.323
Just and true are thy ways, thou King of saints!

00:53:03.883 --> 00:53:07.803
Who shall not fear thee, O Lord, and glorify thy name?

00:53:08.123 --> 00:53:14.443
For thou only art holy, for all nations shall come and worship before thee, for thy judgments

00:53:14.443 --> 00:53:16.263
are made manifest.

00:53:16.823 --> 00:53:23.083
And after that I looked, and behold, the temple of the tabernacle of the testimony in heaven

00:53:23.083 --> 00:53:29.083
was opened, and the seven angels came out of the temple, having the seven plagues, clothed

00:53:29.083 --> 00:53:33.523
in pure and white linen, and having their breasts girded with golden girdles.

00:53:33.863 --> 00:53:40.363
And one of the four beasts gave unto the seven angels seven golden vials, full of the wrath

00:53:40.363 --> 00:53:43.063
of God, who liveth for ever and ever.

00:53:43.463 --> 00:53:49.043
And the temple was filled with smoke from the glory of God and from his power, and no

00:53:49.043 --> 00:53:54.823
was able to enter into the temple till the seven plagues of the seven angels were fulfilled.

00:53:56.263 --> 00:53:58.163
The

00:54:16.773 --> 00:54:21.293
heard a great voice out of the temple

00:54:21.293 --> 00:54:27.653
saying to the seven angels, Go your ways, and pour out the vials of the wrath of God

00:54:27.653 --> 00:54:28.633
upon the earth.

00:54:29.493 --> 00:54:33.313
And the first went, and poured out his vial upon the earth.

00:54:33.753 --> 00:54:38.733
And there fell a noisome and grievous sore upon the men which had the mark of the beast,

00:54:38.953 --> 00:54:41.293
and upon them which worshipped his image.

00:54:42.233 --> 00:54:48.053
And the second angel poured out his vial upon the sea, and it became as the blood of a dead

00:54:48.053 --> 00:54:51.473
man, and every living soul died in the sea.

00:54:51.893 --> 00:54:57.493
And the third angel poured out his vial upon the rivers and fountains of waters, and they

00:54:57.493 --> 00:54:58.573
became blood.

00:54:59.353 --> 00:55:06.493
And I heard the angel of the waters say, Thou art righteous, O Lord, which art, and wast,

00:55:06.713 --> 00:55:09.913
and shalt be, because thou hast judged thus.

00:55:10.553 --> 00:55:15.893
For they have shed the blood of saints and prophets, and thou hast given them blood to

00:55:15.893 --> 00:55:18.053
drink, for they are worthy.

00:55:18.833 --> 00:55:26.233
And I heard another out of the altar say, Even so, Lord God Almighty, true and righteous

00:55:26.233 --> 00:55:27.373
are thy judgments.

00:55:28.433 --> 00:55:34.333
And the fourth angel poured out his vial upon the sun, and power was given unto him to scorch

00:55:34.333 --> 00:55:35.453
men with fire.

00:55:35.893 --> 00:55:41.253
And men were scorched with great heat, and blasphemed the name of God, which hath power

00:55:41.253 --> 00:55:42.613
over these plagues.

00:55:43.053 --> 00:55:45.893
And they repented not to give him glory.

00:55:46.393 --> 00:55:51.793
And the fifth angel poured out his vial upon the seat of the beast, and his kingdom was

00:55:51.793 --> 00:55:57.953
full of darkness, and they gnawed their tongues for pain, and blasphemed the God of heaven

00:55:57.953 --> 00:56:02.753
because of their pains and their sores, and repented not of their deeds.

00:56:03.373 --> 00:56:09.573
And the sixth angel poured out his vial upon the great river Euphrates, and the water thereof

00:56:09.573 --> 00:56:13.613
was dried up, that the way of the kings of the east might be prepared.

00:56:14.253 --> 00:56:19.853
And I saw three unclean spirits like frogs come out of the mouth of the dragon, and out

00:56:19.853 --> 00:56:23.373
of the mouth of the beast, and out of the mouth of the false prophet.

00:56:23.633 --> 00:56:28.933
For they are the spirits of devils, working miracles, which go forth unto the kings of

00:56:28.933 --> 00:56:33.793
the earth and of the whole world, to gather them to the battle of that great day of God

00:56:33.793 --> 00:56:34.333
Almighty.

00:56:35.833 --> 00:56:38.473
Behold, I come as a thief.

00:56:39.213 --> 00:56:45.173
Blessed is he that watcheth, and keepeth his garments, lest he walk naked, and they see

00:56:45.173 --> 00:56:46.073
his shame.

00:56:46.873 --> 00:56:53.213
And he gathered them together into a place called in the Hebrew tongue Armageddon.

00:56:54.213 --> 00:56:59.053
And the seventh angel poured out his vial into the air, and there came a great voice

00:56:59.053 --> 00:57:04.933
out of the temple of heaven, from the throne, saying, It is done.

00:57:05.933 --> 00:57:11.293
And there were voices, and thunders, and lightnings, and there was a great earthquake, such as was

00:57:11.293 --> 00:57:15.913
not since men were upon the earth, so mighty an earthquake, and so great.

00:57:16.313 --> 00:57:21.393
And the great city was divided into three parts, and the cities of the nations fell.

00:57:21.693 --> 00:57:27.233
And great Babylon came in remembrance before God, to give unto her the cup of the wine

00:57:27.233 --> 00:57:29.393
of the fierceness of his wrath.

00:57:29.793 --> 00:57:33.533
And every island fled away, and the mountains were not found.

00:57:34.153 --> 00:57:39.453
And there fell upon men a great hail out of heaven, every stone about the weight of a

00:57:39.453 --> 00:57:46.113
and men blasphemed God because of the plague of the hail, for the plague thereof was exceeding

00:57:46.113 --> 00:57:46.533
great.

00:57:48.673 --> 00:57:50.893
The

00:58:11.795 --> 00:58:17.155
And there came one of the seven angels which had the seven vials, and talked with me, saying

00:58:17.155 --> 00:58:23.875
unto me, Come, Heather, I will shew unto thee the judgment of the great whore that sitteth

00:58:23.875 --> 00:58:29.295
upon many waters, with whom the kings of the earth have committed fornication, and the

00:58:29.295 --> 00:58:33.495
inhabitants of the earth have been made drunk with the wine of her fornication.

00:58:34.215 --> 00:58:41.175
So he carried me away in the spirit into the wilderness, and I saw a woman sit upon a scarlet-coloured

00:58:41.175 --> 00:58:45.815
beast, full of names of blasphemy, having seven heads and ten horns.

00:58:46.295 --> 00:58:51.395
And the woman was arrayed in purple and scarlet colour, and decked with gold and precious

00:58:51.395 --> 00:58:58.575
stones and pearls, having a golden cup in her hand, full of abominations and filthiness of her fornication.

00:58:59.035 --> 00:59:06.655
And upon her forehead was a name written, Mystery, Babylon the Great, the mother of harlots and

00:59:06.655 --> 00:59:08.255
abominations of the earth.

00:59:08.935 --> 00:59:14.035
And I saw the woman drunken with the blood of the saints and with the blood of the martyrs

00:59:14.035 --> 00:59:18.195
of Jesus, and when I saw her, I wondered with great admiration.

00:59:18.935 --> 00:59:23.155
And the angels said unto me, Wherefore didst thou marvel?

00:59:23.495 --> 00:59:28.355
I will tell thee the mystery of the woman and of the beast that carrieth her which hath

00:59:28.355 --> 00:59:30.235
the seven heads and ten horns.

00:59:30.695 --> 00:59:36.355
The beast that thou sawest was, and is not, and shall ascend out of the bottomless pit

00:59:36.355 --> 00:59:37.995
and go into perdition.

00:59:38.295 --> 00:59:46.535
And they that dwell on the earth shall wonder, whose names were not written in the book of

00:59:46.535 --> 00:59:49.735
the beast that was, and is not, and yet is.

00:59:50.315 --> 00:59:52.955
And here is the mind which hath wisdom.

00:59:53.355 --> 00:59:59.455
The seven heads are seven mountains on which the woman sitteth, and there are seven kings.

00:59:59.735 --> 01:00:04.015
Five are fallen, and one is, and the other is not yet come.

01:00:04.395 --> 01:00:07.655
And when he cometh, he must continue a short space.

01:00:08.155 --> 01:00:14.435
And the beast that was, and is not, even he is the eighth, and is of the seven, and goeth

01:00:14.435 --> 01:00:15.635
into perdition.

01:00:16.015 --> 01:00:21.615
And the ten horns which thou sawest are ten kings which have received no kingdom as yet,

01:00:21.835 --> 01:00:25.275
but receive power as kings one hour with the beast.

01:00:25.895 --> 01:00:30.455
These have one mind, and shall give their power and strength unto the beast.

01:00:30.955 --> 01:00:35.335
These shall make war with the lamb, and the lamb shall overcome them.

01:00:35.455 --> 01:00:41.375
For he is lord of lords and king of kings, and they that are with him are called and

01:00:41.375 --> 01:00:43.035
chosen, and faithful.

01:00:44.275 --> 01:00:49.435
And he sayeth unto me, The waters which thou sawest where the whore

01:00:49.435 --> 01:00:53.655
sitteth are peoples and multitudes and nations and tongues.

01:00:54.035 --> 01:00:59.515
And the ten horns which thou sawest upon the beast, these shall hate the whore, and shall

01:00:59.515 --> 01:01:04.475
make her desolate and naked, and shall eat her flesh, and burn her with fire.

01:01:04.855 --> 01:01:10.575
For God hath put in their hearts to fulfil his will, and to agree, and give their kingdom

01:01:10.575 --> 01:01:13.955
unto the beast until the words of God shall be fulfilled.

01:01:14.395 --> 01:01:19.815
And the woman which thou sawest is that great city which reigneth over the kings of the

01:01:19.815 --> 01:01:20.255
earth.

01:01:30.003 --> 01:01:50.763
18. And after these things I saw another angel come down from heaven, having great power,

01:01:51.043 --> 01:01:56.563
and the earth was lightened with his glory, and he cried mightily with a strong voice,

01:01:57.803 --> 01:02:04.503
Babylon the Great is fallen, is fallen, and is become the habitation of devils, and the

01:02:04.503 --> 01:02:10.763
hold of every foul spirit, and a cage of every unclean and hateful bird. For all nations

01:02:10.763 --> 01:02:15.223
have drunk of the wine of the wrath of her fornication, and the kings of the earth have

01:02:15.223 --> 01:02:20.343
committed fornication with her, and the merchants of the earth are waxed rich through the abundance

01:02:20.343 --> 01:02:27.903
of her delicacies. And I heard another voice from heaven saying, Come out of her, my people,

01:02:28.083 --> 01:02:34.263
that ye be not partakers of her sins, and that ye receive not of her plagues. For her sins have

01:02:34.263 --> 01:02:40.923
reached unto heaven, and God hath remembered her iniquities. Reward her even as she rewarded you,

01:02:41.123 --> 01:02:47.123
and double unto her double according to her works. In the cup which she hath filled, fill to her

01:02:47.123 --> 01:02:54.223
double. How much she hath glorified herself, and lived deliciously. So much torment and sorrow give

01:02:54.223 --> 01:03:01.563
her, for she saith in her heart, I sit a queen, and am no widow, and shall see no sorrow. Therefore

01:03:01.563 --> 01:03:07.663
shall her plagues come in one day, death and mourning and famine, and she shall be utterly

01:03:07.663 --> 01:03:14.463
burned with fire. For strong is the Lord God who judgeth her. And the kings of the earth who have

01:03:14.463 --> 01:03:20.543
committed fornication, and lived deliciously with her, shall bewail her, and lament for her, when they

01:03:20.543 --> 01:03:27.103
shall see the smoke of her burning, standing afar off for the fear of her torment, saying, Alas,

01:03:28.303 --> 01:03:36.783
alas, that great city Babylon, that mighty city, for in one hour is thy judgment come. And the

01:03:36.783 --> 01:03:43.243
merchants of the earth shall weep and mourn over her, for no man buyeth their merchandise any more.

01:03:43.243 --> 01:03:50.323
The merchandise of gold, and silver, and precious stones, and of pearls, and fine linen, and purple,

01:03:50.483 --> 01:03:57.303
and silk, and scarlet, and all fine wood, and all manner vessels of ivory, and all manner vessels of

01:03:57.303 --> 01:04:03.963
most precious wood, and of brass, and iron, and marble, and cinnamon, and odors, and ointments,

01:04:04.223 --> 01:04:11.103
and frankincense, and wine, and oil, and fine flour, and wheat, and beasts, and sheep, and horses,

01:04:11.103 --> 01:04:18.343
and chariots, and slaves, and souls of men. And the fruits that thy soul lusted after are departed

01:04:18.343 --> 01:04:24.343
from thee, and all things which were dainty and goodly are departed from thee, and thou shalt find

01:04:24.343 --> 01:04:31.283
them no more at all. The merchants of these things which were made rich by her shall stand afar off

01:04:31.283 --> 01:04:39.843
for the fear of her torment, weeping and wailing, and saying, Alas, alas, that great city that was

01:04:39.843 --> 01:04:47.003
clothed in fine linen, and purple, and scarlet, and decked with gold, and precious stones, and pearls,

01:04:47.323 --> 01:04:55.083
for in one hour so great riches is come to naught. And every shipmaster, and all the company in ships,

01:04:55.463 --> 01:05:01.663
and sailors, and as many as trade by sea, stood afar off, and cried when they saw the smoke of

01:05:01.663 --> 01:05:09.603
her burning, saying, What city is like unto this great city? And they cast dust on their heads,

01:05:09.603 --> 01:05:19.163
and cried, weeping and wailing, saying, Alas, alas, that great city wherein were made rich all that

01:05:19.163 --> 01:05:27.343
had ships in the sea by reason of her costliness, for in one hour is she made desolate. Rejoice over

01:05:27.343 --> 01:05:33.223
her, thou heaven, and ye holy apostles and prophets, for God hath avenged you on her.

01:05:34.023 --> 01:05:40.503
And a mighty angel took up a stone like a great millstone, and cast it into the sea, saying,

01:05:41.223 --> 01:05:48.463
Thus with violence shall that great city Babylon be thrown down, and shall be found no more at all,

01:05:48.743 --> 01:05:54.883
and the voice of harpers, and musicians, and of pipers, and trumpeters shall be heard no more

01:05:54.883 --> 01:06:01.483
at all in thee, and no craftsman of whatsoever craft he be shall be found any more in thee,

01:06:01.483 --> 01:06:07.463
and the sound of a millstone shall be heard no more at all in thee, and the light of a candle

01:06:07.463 --> 01:06:13.243
shall shine no more at all in thee, and the voice of the bridegroom, and of the bride shall be heard

01:06:13.243 --> 01:06:19.643
no more at all in thee, for thy merchants were the great men of the earth, for by thy sorceries were

01:06:19.643 --> 01:06:26.523
all nations deceived, and in her was found the blood of prophets, and of saints, and of all that

01:06:26.523 --> 01:06:28.343
slain upon the earth.

01:06:29.843 --> 01:06:32.023
The

01:06:53.708 --> 01:06:58.548
And after these things I heard a great voice of much people in heaven, saying,

01:07:00.128 --> 01:07:05.928
Alleluia! Salvation and glory and honour and power unto the Lord our God!

01:07:06.348 --> 01:07:13.868
For true and righteous are His judgments, for He hath judged the great whore which did corrupt the earth with her fornication,

01:07:14.148 --> 01:07:17.588
and hath avenged the blood of His servants at her hand.

01:07:18.508 --> 01:07:19.788
And again they said,

01:07:20.888 --> 01:07:24.988
Alleluia! And her smoke rose up for ever and ever!

01:07:24.988 --> 01:07:33.128
And the four and twenty elders and the four beasts fell down and worshipped God that sat on the throne, saying,

01:07:34.288 --> 01:07:40.188
Amen! Alleluia! And a voice came out of the throne, saying,

01:07:40.988 --> 01:07:46.708
Praise our God, all ye His servants, and ye that fear Him both small and great!

01:07:46.708 --> 01:07:55.668
And I heard as it were the voice of a great multitude, and as the voice of many waters, and as the voice of mighty thunderings, saying,

01:07:57.568 --> 01:08:07.208
Alleluia! For the Lord God omnipotent reigneth! Let us be glad and rejoice and give honour to Him, for the marriage of the Lamb is come,

01:08:07.428 --> 01:08:15.108
and His wife hath made herself ready, and to her was granted that she should be arrayed in fine linen, clean and white.

01:08:15.108 --> 01:08:18.808
For the fine linen is the righteousness of saints.

01:08:19.368 --> 01:08:26.108
And He saith unto me, Right, blessed are they which are called unto the marriage supper of the Lamb!

01:08:26.668 --> 01:08:31.168
And He saith unto me, These are the true sayings of God!

01:08:31.728 --> 01:08:36.008
And I fell at His feet to worship Him, and He said unto me,

01:08:36.008 --> 01:08:43.588
See thou, do it not! I am thy fellow-servant, and of thy brethren that have the testimony of Jesus!

01:08:44.208 --> 01:08:49.028
Worship God, for the testimony of Jesus is the spirit of prophecy!

01:08:50.048 --> 01:08:54.968
And I saw heaven opened, and behold, a white horse!

01:08:55.408 --> 01:09:02.708
And He that sat upon Him was called Faithful and True, and in righteousness He doth judge and make war.

01:09:02.708 --> 01:09:12.108
His eyes were as a flame of fire, and on His head were many crowns, and He had a name written that no man knew but He Himself.

01:09:12.708 --> 01:09:20.528
And He was clothed with a vesture dipped in blood, and His name is called the Word of God.

01:09:21.048 --> 01:09:27.628
And the armies which were in heaven followed Him upon white horses, clothed in fine linen, white and clean.

01:09:27.628 --> 01:09:36.548
And out of His mouth goeth a sharp sword, that with it He should smite the nations, and He shall rule them with a rod of iron.

01:09:36.948 --> 01:09:41.628
And He treadeth the winepress of the fierceness and wrath of Almighty God.

01:09:42.148 --> 01:09:50.588
And He hath on His vesture and on His thigh a name written, King of Kings and Lord of Lords.

01:09:51.488 --> 01:10:00.168
And I saw an angel standing in the sun, and He cried with a loud voice, saying to all the fowls that fly in the midst of heaven,

01:10:01.068 --> 01:10:10.368
Come and gather yourselves together unto the supper of the great God, that ye may eat the flesh of kings, and the flesh of captains,

01:10:10.408 --> 01:10:20.068
and the flesh of mighty men, and the flesh of horses, and of them that sit on them, and the flesh of all men, both free and bond, both small and great.

01:10:20.688 --> 01:10:29.668
And I saw the beast, and the kings of the earth and their armies gathered together to make war against Him that sat on the horse, and against His army.

01:10:30.088 --> 01:10:38.688
And the beast was taken, and with Him the false prophet that wrought miracles before Him, with which He deceived them that had received the mark of the beast,

01:10:38.908 --> 01:10:40.828
and them that worshipped His image.

01:10:40.828 --> 01:10:50.148
These both were cast alive into a lake of fire burning with brimstone, and the remnant were slain with the sword of Him that sat upon the horse,

01:10:50.528 --> 01:10:55.888
which sword proceeded out of His mouth, and all the fowls were filled with their flesh.

01:11:18.546 --> 01:11:24.126
And I saw an angel come down from heaven, having the key of the bottomless pit and a

01:11:24.126 --> 01:11:29.446
great chain in his hand. And he laid hold on the dragon, that old serpent, which is

01:11:29.446 --> 01:11:35.426
the devil and Satan, and bound him a thousand years, and cast him into the bottomless pit

01:11:35.426 --> 01:11:40.926
and shut him up, and set a seal upon him, that he should deceive the nations no more

01:11:40.926 --> 01:11:46.566
till the thousand years should be fulfilled. And after that he must be loosed a little

01:11:46.566 --> 01:11:53.126
season. And I saw thrones, and they sat upon them, and judgment was given unto them. And

01:11:53.126 --> 01:11:57.446
I saw the souls of them that were beheaded for the witness of Jesus, and for the word

01:11:57.446 --> 01:12:02.926
of God, and which had not worshipped the beast neither his image, neither had received his

01:12:02.926 --> 01:12:09.306
mark upon their foreheads, or in their hands. And they lived and reigned with Christ a thousand

01:12:09.306 --> 01:12:14.546
years, but the rest of the dead lived not again until the thousand years were finished.

01:12:15.126 --> 01:12:17.646
This is the first resurrection.

01:12:18.736 --> 01:12:24.526
Blessed and holy is he that hath part in the first resurrection. On such the second death

01:12:24.526 --> 01:12:30.026
hath no power. But they shall be priests of God and of Christ, and shall reign with

01:12:30.026 --> 01:12:36.106
him a thousand years. And when the thousand years are expired, Satan shall be loosed out

01:12:36.106 --> 01:12:40.766
of his prison, and shall go out to deceive the nations which are in the four quarters

01:12:40.766 --> 01:12:47.226
of the earth, Gog and Magog, to gather them together to battle, the number of whom is

01:12:47.226 --> 01:12:54.506
as the sand of the sea. And they went up on the breadth of the earth, and compassed the

01:12:54.506 --> 01:13:01.226
city, and fire came down from God out of heaven, and devoured them. And the devil that deceived

01:13:01.226 --> 01:13:06.546
them was cast into the lake of fire and brimstone, where the beast and the false prophet are,

01:13:06.846 --> 01:13:14.786
and shall be tormented day and night, for ever and ever. And I saw a great white throne,

01:13:15.286 --> 01:13:20.986
and him that sat on it, from whose face the earth and the heaven fled away, and there

01:13:20.986 --> 01:13:27.766
was found no place for them. And I saw the dead, small and great, stand before God, and

01:13:27.766 --> 01:13:34.266
the books were opened. And another book was opened, which is the Book of Life, and the

01:13:34.266 --> 01:13:38.766
dead were judged out of those things which were written in the books according to their

01:13:38.766 --> 01:13:44.026
works. And the sea gave up the dead which were in it, and death and hell delivered up

01:13:44.026 --> 01:13:48.806
the dead which were in them, and they were judged every man according to their works.

01:13:49.446 --> 01:13:56.886
And death and hell were cast into the lake of fire. This is the second death, and whosoever

01:13:57.146 --> 01:14:02.366
was not found written in the Book of Life was cast into the lake of fire.

01:14:26.922 --> 01:14:35.042
21. And I saw a new heaven and a new earth, for the first heaven and the first earth were

01:14:35.042 --> 01:14:45.942
and there was no more sea. And I, John, saw the holy city, new Jerusalem, coming down

01:14:45.942 --> 01:14:52.142
from God out of heaven, prepared as a bride adorned for her husband. And I heard a great

01:14:52.142 --> 01:15:01.162
voice out of heaven saying, Behold, the tabernacle of God is with men, and he will dwell with

01:15:01.162 --> 01:15:07.922
them, and they shall be his people, and God himself shall be with them and be their God.

01:15:08.222 --> 01:15:14.722
And God shall wipe away all tears from their eyes, and there shall be no more death, neither

01:15:14.722 --> 01:15:21.942
sorrow nor crying, neither shall there be any more pain, for the former things are passed

01:15:21.942 --> 01:15:32.402
away. And he that sat upon the throne said, Behold, I make all things new. And he said

01:15:32.402 --> 01:15:43.742
unto me, Write, for these words are true and faithful. And he said unto me, It is done.

01:15:44.562 --> 01:15:51.762
I am Alpha and Omega, the beginning and the end. I will give unto him that is a thirst

01:15:51.762 --> 01:15:58.462
of the fountain of the water of life freely. He that overcometh shall inherit all things,

01:15:58.882 --> 01:16:06.942
and I will be his God, and he shall be my son. But the fearful and unbelieving and the

01:16:06.942 --> 01:16:13.902
abominable and murderers and whoremongers and sorcerers and idolaters and all liars

01:16:13.902 --> 01:16:19.722
shall have their part in the lake which burneth with fire and brimstone, which is the second

01:16:19.722 --> 01:16:26.422
death. And there came unto me one of the seven angels which had the seven vials full

01:16:26.422 --> 01:16:34.202
of the seven last plagues, and talked with me, saying, Come hither, I will shew thee

01:16:34.202 --> 01:16:41.342
the bride, the Lamb's wife. And he carried me away in the spirit to a great and high

01:16:41.342 --> 01:16:48.002
mountain and shewed me that great city, the holy Jerusalem, descending out of heaven from

01:16:48.002 --> 01:16:55.442
God, having the glory of God. And her light was like unto a stone most precious, even

01:16:55.442 --> 01:17:02.842
like a jasper stone, clear as crystal, and had a wall great and high, and had twelve

01:17:02.842 --> 01:17:08.982
gates, and at the gates twelve angels, and names written thereon which are the names

01:17:08.982 --> 01:17:16.342
of the twelve tribes of the children of Israel. On the east three gates, on the north three

01:17:16.342 --> 01:17:23.382
gates, on the south three gates, and on the west three gates. And the wall of the city

01:17:23.382 --> 01:17:30.822
had twelve foundations, and in them the names of the twelve apostles of the Lamb. And he

01:17:30.822 --> 01:17:36.302
that talked with me had a golden reed to measure the city and the gates thereof and the wall

01:17:36.302 --> 01:17:43.162
thereof. And the city lieth foursquare, and the length is as large as the breadth, and

01:17:43.162 --> 01:17:49.462
he measured the city with the reed, twelve thousand furlongs. The length and the breadth

01:17:49.462 --> 01:17:55.522
and the height of it are equal. And he measured the wall thereof, and hundred and forty and

01:17:55.522 --> 01:18:01.502
four cubits according to the measure of a man, that is, of the angel. And the building

01:18:01.502 --> 01:18:08.742
of the wall of it was of jasper, and the city was pure gold, like unto clear glass. And

01:18:08.742 --> 01:18:14.322
the foundations of the wall of the city were garnished with all manner of precious stones.

01:18:14.842 --> 01:18:22.342
The first foundation was jasper, the second sapphire, the third a chalcedony, the fourth

01:18:22.562 --> 01:18:30.742
an emerald, the fifth sardonyx, the sixth sardius, the seventh chrysolite, the eighth

01:18:30.742 --> 01:18:38.722
beryl, the ninth a topaz, the tenth a chrysoprasis, the eleventh a jasonth, the twelfth a chrysolite,

01:18:38.742 --> 01:18:46.982
an amethyst. And the twelve gates were twelve pearls. Every several gate was of one pearl,

01:18:47.342 --> 01:18:54.682
and the street of the city was pure gold, as it were transparent glass. And I saw no

01:18:54.682 --> 01:19:00.242
temple therein, for the Lord God Almighty and the Lamb are the temple of it. And the

01:19:00.242 --> 01:19:05.762
city had no need of the sun, neither of the moon, to shine in it, for the glory of God

01:19:05.762 --> 01:19:11.862
did lighten it, and the Lamb is the light thereof. And the nations of them which are

01:19:11.862 --> 01:19:16.922
saved shall walk in the light of it, and the kings of the earth do bring their glory and

01:19:16.922 --> 01:19:23.062
honor into it. And the gates of it shall not be shut at all by day, for there shall be

01:19:23.062 --> 01:19:29.722
no night there. And they shall bring the glory and honor of the nations into it, and there

01:19:29.722 --> 01:19:35.842
shall in no wise enter into it anything that defileth, neither whatsoever worketh abomination

01:19:35.842 --> 01:19:41.962
or maketh a lie, but they which are written in the Lamb's Book of Life.

01:20:08.907 --> 01:20:15.527
And he shewed me a pure river of water of life, clear as crystal, proceeding out of

01:20:15.527 --> 01:20:21.207
the throne of God and of the Lamb, in the midst of the street of it, and on either side

01:20:21.207 --> 01:20:27.567
of the river was there the tree of life, which bear twelve manner of fruits, and yielded

01:20:27.567 --> 01:20:29.107
her fruit every month.

01:20:29.587 --> 01:20:36.747
And the leaves of the tree were for the healing of the nations, and there shall be no more

01:20:36.747 --> 01:20:37.187
curse.

01:20:37.547 --> 01:20:42.947
But the throne of God and of the Lamb shall be in it, and his servants shall serve him,

01:20:42.947 --> 01:20:49.547
and they shall see his face, and his name shall be in their foreheads.

01:20:49.547 --> 01:20:55.667
And there shall be no night there, and they need no candle, neither light of the sun,

01:20:55.927 --> 01:21:01.707
for the Lord God giveth them light, and they shall reign for ever and ever.

01:21:02.447 --> 01:21:10.447
And he said unto me, These sayings are faithful and true, and the Lord God of the holy prophets

01:21:10.447 --> 01:21:17.027
sent his angel to shew unto his servants the things which must shortly be done.

01:21:18.547 --> 01:21:21.727
Behold, I come quickly.

01:21:22.847 --> 01:21:26.847
Blessed is he that keepeth the sayings of the prophecy of this book.

01:21:27.627 --> 01:21:32.067
And I, John, saw these things, and heard them.

01:21:32.447 --> 01:21:38.467
And when I had heard and seen, I fell down to worship before the feet of the angel which

01:21:38.467 --> 01:21:39.887
me these things.

01:21:40.407 --> 01:21:48.207
Then sayeth he unto me, See thou do it not, for I am thy fellow-servant, and of thy brethren

01:21:48.207 --> 01:21:51.727
the prophets, and of them which keep the sayings of this book.

01:21:52.307 --> 01:21:53.707
Worship God.

01:21:54.487 --> 01:22:01.227
And he sayeth unto me, Seal not the sayings of the prophecy of this book, for the time

01:22:01.227 --> 01:22:02.407
is at hand.

01:22:02.967 --> 01:22:06.407
He that is unjust, let him be unjust still.

01:22:06.827 --> 01:22:10.187
And he which is filthy, let him be filthy still.

01:22:10.527 --> 01:22:13.707
And he that is righteous, let him be righteous still.

01:22:14.087 --> 01:22:17.587
And he that is holy, let him be holy still.

01:22:18.967 --> 01:22:22.267
And behold, I come quickly.

01:22:22.627 --> 01:22:27.927
And my reward is with me, to give every man according as his work shall be.

01:22:28.727 --> 01:22:34.987
I am Alpha and Omega, the beginning and the end, the first and the last.

01:22:36.007 --> 01:22:42.207
Blessed are they that do his commandments, that they may have right to the tree of life,

01:22:42.647 --> 01:22:45.947
and may enter in through the gates into the city.

01:22:46.507 --> 01:22:54.127
For without are dogs, and sorcerers, and whoremongers, and murderers, and idolaters, and whosoever

01:22:54.127 --> 01:22:55.907
loveth and maketh a lie.

01:22:57.367 --> 01:23:04.127
I, Jesus, have sent mine angel to testify unto you these things in the churches.

01:23:04.787 --> 01:23:10.607
I am the root and the offspring of David, and the bright and morning star.

01:23:11.747 --> 01:23:20.527
And the Spirit and the Bride say, Come, and let him that heareth say, Come, and let him

01:23:20.527 --> 01:23:27.867
that is a thirst come, and whosoever will, let him take the water of life freely.

01:23:28.927 --> 01:23:34.247
For I testify unto every man that heareth the words of the prophecy of this book.

01:23:34.627 --> 01:23:40.827
If any man shall add unto these things, God shall add unto him the plagues that are written

01:23:40.827 --> 01:23:41.927
in this book.

01:23:42.167 --> 01:23:48.687
And if any man shall take away from the words of the book of this prophecy, God shall take

01:23:48.687 --> 01:23:54.947
away his part out of the book of life, and out of the holy city, and from the things

01:23:54.947 --> 01:23:57.007
which are written in this book.

01:23:57.907 --> 01:24:05.047
He which testifieth these things saith, Surely I come quickly.

01:24:06.567 --> 01:24:07.127
Amen.

01:24:08.427 --> 01:24:11.567
Even so, Come, Lord Jesus.

01:24:12.447 --> 01:24:18.167
The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ be with you all.

01:24:19.207 --> 01:24:20.007
Amen.

01:24:41.567 --> 01:24:42.387
Nebraska.
